answer: What were the return on average assets and ROWC of Halliburton co. and other companies in the energy sector from Apr 2016 to Jul 2017 compared to their Gross Profit Margin and CROAFA?

question: Etung total metrik sing ana ing kabeh telung pitakonan.

Pitakon basa ngoko endi sing cocog karo panjaluk terstruktur sing nyakup wektu paling suwe?
answer: What were the return on average assets and ROWC of Halliburton co. and other companies in the energy sector from Apr 2016 to Jul 2017 compared to their Gross Profit Margin and CROAFA?

answer: Cash Return on Average Fixed Assets

question: Nggo pitakon Amcor plc, pinten persen metrik kabeh sing kasebut ing 'Structured Data Request' kanthi eksplisit ngemot tembung 'Cash'?

Nek pitakonan basa kanggo Adobe ditambah pitakonan 'Return on Working Capital', kepriye daftare metrik ing 'Structured Data Request' bakal diowahi, nganggo informasi saka pitakonan Halliburton minangka conto?
answer: Bagian metrik ing 'Structured Data Request' bakal dianyari kanggo nglebokake 'Return on Working Capital' lan komponen sing gegandhengan saka pitakonan Halliburton. Iki bakal tegese nambah 'Return on Working Capital; Net income; Working capital' menyang dhaptar sing wis ana, dadi: (Sales Revenue; Total Revenue; Economic Value Added; Net operating profit after tax (NOPAT); Cost of capital; Return on Working Capital; Net income; Working capital).

question: Ndeleng data sing wis kasedhiya, ana gayutan apa antarane kerumitan pitakon basa alami 'Query' lan jumlah metrik sing ditemtokake ing 'Structured Data Request'?
answer: Katoné ana gayutan positif. Rong pitakon sing luwih rumit (kanggo Amcor lan Halliburton) cocog karo jumlah metrik sing luwih akeh ing panjaluk terstrukturé (masing-masing 14 lan 12) dibandhingake karo pitakon sing luwih gampang kanggo Adobe, sing mung duwé 5 metrik. Iki nuduhaké yèn nalika kedalaman analitis pitakon pangguna saya mundhak, muatan data sing dibutuhaké uga saya mundhak.

question: Kolom endi sing fungsine kanggo mbongkar kueri basa alami dadi format semi-terstruktur sing kanthi jelas nyathet perusahaan, metrik utama, sub-metrik sing gegandhengan, lan kerangka wektu sing dijaluk?
Ndeloken informasi wektu ning kolom 'Required Data' lan 'Structured Data Request'. Ono ora pitakonan sing kolom loro mau wektune beda? Nek onok, sebutno pitakonan lan jelasno bedane.
answer: Iyo, pitakonan Amcor plc katon bedo nemen. Ning bagian 'Required Data' iku nyebutke wektu 'sakwulan-wulan wingi', dene 'Structured Data Request' sing cocok nyebutke wektu sing luwih cendek, 7 dina yaiku '(7/1/2024 - 7/7/2024)'. Kaloro pitakonan liyane katon konsisten wektune antarane kolom.
